These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, golf, swimming
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, turkish, egyptian
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the turkish##1
5. the egyptian is between the indonesian and the turkish##2
6. the person who's sport is swimming is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | swimming | climbing     | golf | cycling |
| Nationality     | chinese     | turkish | egyptian  | indonesian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: marseilles, paris, berlin, rome
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, iris, marigold
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | marseilles | paris    | rome     | berlin  |
| Flower     | daisy    | iris | lily | marigold |

