.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, epic, action, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian, japanese, colombian
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the japanese is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | action   | horror  | martial-arts |
| Nationality           | brazilian | colombian | japanese | pakistani  |

