.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, accountant, musician, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, jazz, reggae, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the musician##1
2. the writer is between the teacher and the fan of reggae##2
3. the writer is on the left or right of the musician##3
4. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
5. the teacher is on the right of the accountant##1
6. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Job         | accountant | teacher | writer | musician  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | pop   | classical  | reggae |

