.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, aconite, marigold
House: cape-cod, victorian, gothic-revival, craftsman
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the craftsman house is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | zinnia    | tulip   | aconite | marigold    |
| House      | victorian | cape-cod | gothic-revival       | craftsman |

