.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
House: palace, ranch-style, victorian, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, blue, red, azure
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the person who likes red is between the person who likes azure and the victorian house##2
3. the person who likes white is between the person who likes red and the palace house##2
4. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| House    | palace | victorian | townhouse | ranch-style |
| Color   | blue | white  | red    | azure  |

