.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, oliveros, vegafina
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
5. the owner of the goldfish is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the fish and the vegafina-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | davidoff | vegafina | oliveros | cain     |
| Pet     | cat | hedgehog  | goldfish   | fish |

