.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
City: new-york, edinburgh, paris, london
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, designer, librarian, social-worker
1. the electrician is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to london is the designer##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the designer is on the left or right of the librarian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| City         | london | paris | new-york | edinburgh   |
| Job   | designer | librarian | electrician      | social-worker |

