.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, apricot, lettuce, asparagus
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, go, whist
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
3. the person playing whist is the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
5. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating apricot is between the person playing billiard and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food     | peas | apricot   | lettuce      | asparagus      |
| Game   | billiard     | go | mah-jongg | whist |

