.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, ice-hockey, weightlifting
City: prague, edinburgh, hannover, new-york
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | badminton | ice-hockey | weightlifting    | skiing      |
| City   | hannover       | new-york       | edinburgh | prague |

