.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, chef, photographer, journalist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, volleyball, tennis
1. the paramedic is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the chef is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the photographer##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is the paramedic##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Job         | chef | journalist | photographer | paramedic |
| Sport   | tennis     | cycling       | cricket   | volleyball      |

