.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, chinchilla, mouse
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge
1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Pet   | lizard | mouse | chinchilla | bird |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | backgammon   | bridge | chess     |

