.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, basketball, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Sport      | sailing | parkour    | biathlon  | basketball |
| Transport   | bus       | ship | snowmobile | quad-bike  |

