The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, soccer, sailing
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Cigar   | swisher | siglo  | game  | ritmeester |
| Sport           | cricket    | sailing | soccer | climbing |

