1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | october        | april       | may   | march |
| Beverage    | mirinda | tea | almond-milk | hot-chocolate  |

