.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, bridge, scrabble
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, spanish, japanese
1. the spanish is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is the japanese##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the australian is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the spanish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Game   | backgammon     | billiard     | bridge          | scrabble |
| Nationality      | australian | argentine | japanese | spanish  |

 